    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable entry point or a hands-on project car? This vehicle is honestly in poor condition \u2014 you'll notice visible wear both inside and out, and there are mechanical issues that will need attention before it's road-ready. That said, it's a great opportunity for a mechanically savvy buyer or someone who loves a good restoration challenge! Priced to reflect its current state, so what you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises here.",
