    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives, but has some mechanical issues that will likely need attention in the near future. The exterior shows visible wear including scratches and minor dents. The interior has noticeable wear but is functional.",
      "price": 15500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and I want to give any potential buyer a complete and honest picture of what to expect. This car is in exceptional, like-new shape \u2014 it is one of the finest examples you will find on the used market. The exterior paint is flawless, with no scratches, chips, or dents visible anywhere on the body. The interior is immaculate: all surfaces are clean, the upholstery shows no wear, and every button, knob, and screen functions exactly as it did when the car left the factory. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, with no unusual noises, leaks, or warning lights. All mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, and cooling \u2014 are in top working order. The tires have excellent tread remaining and are evenly worn. This is a turn-key vehicle that requires nothing before driving; a buyer can expect a truly premium used-car experience with this one.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Honest Deal Alert: A Budget Buy for the Right Buyer! \ud83d\udd27\n\nWe believe in straight talk, so here it is: this vehicle is in poor condition and priced to reflect that honestly. It has seen better days \u2014 expect wear, imperfections, and likely some mechanical attention needed \u2014 but for a savvy buyer, a hands-on DIYer, or someone needing basic transportation on a tight budget, this could be just the opportunity you're looking for! Everything is priced fairly given its current state, so you know exactly what you're getting. Come take a look and decide for yourself!",
      "price": 5000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition at an honest price of $17,500. The exterior shows the expected signs of regular use \u2014 you'll notice visible scratches, a few minor dents or dings, and some areas where the paint has dulled or faded. The interior is similarly worn, with scuffs on surfaces and upholstery that reflects years of everyday driving. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it is not without its quirks \u2014 minor issues may be present and should be expected at this price point. This is a solid, honest vehicle for a buyer who wants reliable transportation without paying for a pristine finish. What you see is what you get, and the price reflects that straightforwardly.",
      "price": 17500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "This is the one you've been waiting for. Presented in absolutely flawless condition, this vehicle is a rare find in today's market \u2014 every panel, every surface, and every mechanical component reflects meticulous care from day one. The interior is immaculate, free of wear, odors, or blemishes, while the exterior shines with a deep, showroom-quality finish. Starts, drives, and stops with the confidence of a vehicle that has never been neglected. Full service history available, and it's ready to go without a single item on your to-do list. Serious buyers will recognize immediately that opportunities like this don't last. Come see it in person \u2014 we're confident it will exceed your expectations.",
      "price": 47900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I'm so excited to share this absolute gem with you today. This beauty is truly in mint condition \u2014 she's been garage-kept, lovingly maintained, and treated like a member of the family. Every time I take her out, heads turn and I honestly hate to see her go, but it's time for someone new to enjoy her! The paint still has that showroom shine, the interior is spotless (we're talking not a crumb in sight!), and she runs like a dream. No funny smells, no weird noises \u2014 just pure, smooth driving pleasure. I'm the kind of seller who wants you to drive away smiling, so I'm pricing her fairly to make this a no-brainer deal. Come take a look in person \u2014 I promise you won't be disappointed. Serious inquiries only, and I'm happy to answer any questions honestly. Let's get you behind the wheel! \ud83d\ude0a",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "2019 Ford Mustang GT \u2014 Presenting an exceptionally well-sorted example of Ford's iconic pony car, this 5.0L Coyote V8 specimen delivers a factory-rated 460 horsepower through a smooth-shifting 6-speed manual transmission with a short-throw shifter feel that remains crisp and precise. The drivetrain exhibits zero slack \u2014 clutch engagement is confident, throttle response is immediate, and the limited-slip differential hooks up cleanly out of corners. Suspension geometry is tight with no perceptible play in the front control arm bushings or rear IRS components. Brake pedal feel is firm and progressive, suggesting rotors and pads are well within service life. Exterior finish shows deep, consistent gloss with panel gaps that are factory-spec uniform. Interior surfaces are free of wear patterns \u2014 the leather bolsters, steering wheel, and shift knob show virtually no contact fatigue. All HVAC, infotainment, and electrical systems function as designed. This is a driver's car in driver's condition \u2014 sorted, strong, and ready to perform.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    }
  ],
